        {
            "title": "摩根士丹利:聯準會下週料將維持利率不變",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/lLdBaG87BBpyRsw_qunzPQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/STOCK-EXCHANGE-RUSSIAN-TRADING-SYSTEMS_M_1440048891.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - 摩根士丹利表示,<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"聯準會\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:聯準會;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/聯準會\">聯準會</a>預計將在下週的政策會議上維持利率不變,該行預期央行將「維持觀望並保留寬鬆傾向」,儘管近期面臨油價推動的通膨壓力。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">首席美國經濟學家Michael Gapen在報告中寫道,該行仍預期聯準會官員的中位數預測為今年降息一次、明年降息一次,將終端利率維持在3.0%-3.25%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Gapen表示:「油價衝擊應該意味著整體通膨預測會走高,但模型和過去聯準會官員的言論顯示,聯準會將忽略能源價格壓力。」</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-2da22347-cd67-3e61-8908-73560dd78de4-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該行預期聯準會將維持利率不變,並有三位官員持反對意見支持降息,高於1月的兩位。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Gapen指出,理事Bowman、Waller和Miran均已表態支持降息。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">他寫道:「我們高度確信聯準會不會以升息回應」,並補充說適當的政策「要求聯準會『忽略』能源價格壓力……並維持觀望,或在經濟活動走弱時降息。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">更新後的預測應會顯示整體通膨走高、經濟成長放緩,但點陣圖維持不變。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在市場方面,摩根士丹利建議對美國公債存續期間採取中性立場,繼續做好2年期SOFR交換利差,並持續接收6月FOMC OIS。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在貨幣方面,該行認為若主席Jerome Powell強調聯準會正忽略能源驅動的通膨,美元將面臨下行風險,儘管「石油市場發展」仍將是外匯交易的核心。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%91%A9%E6%A0%B9%E5%A3%AB%E4%B8%B9%E5%88%A9-%E8%81%AF%E6%BA%96%E6%9C%83%E4%B8%8B%E9%80%B1%E6%96%99%E5%B0%87%E7%B6%AD%E6%8C%81%E5%88%A9%E7%8E%87%E4%B8%8D%E8%AE%8A-152820901.html",
