        {
            "title": "伊朗新任最高領袖哈梅內伊受傷且「毀容」",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"伊朗新任最高領袖哈梅內伊受傷且「毀容」\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/.6SL87k7eYACLNbm9_bQ6g--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-03/8a817940-1e1a-11f1-9fc7-10e013523bd5\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">伊朗新任最高領袖哈梅內伊受傷且「毀容」</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
